              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/30539871/" class="">帕拉墨得斯之死</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ferkmavie/" class=" " title="阿特拉斯抠抠脚">阿特拉斯抠抠脚</a>
                (Farewell Nimoy)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
